1997 when the moderate president of the opposition Socialist party Presdent Fatos Nano changed the country into a new mode of social justice and development with laws that for first time separated the political power from the concentration of wealth in a democratic way. The reliance to unemploy headedness to gain power expressed by the party process of specific motives on the bases of provinces, is a treason to democracy and freedoms .The practice of dictatorship is created by small minds in power in the party and the people not to succeed in achieving objectives.
